  <entry>
    <title>python自动化批量下载外文文献</title>
    <url>/2020/05/01/python%E8%87%AA%E5%8A%A8%E5%8C%96%E6%89%B9%E9%87%8F%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD%E5%A4%96%E6%96%87%E6%96%87%E7%8C%AE/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="Part-1：-学习别人造好的轮子记录笔记"><a href="#Part-1：-学习别人造好的轮子记录笔记" class="headerlink" title="Part 1： 学习别人造好的轮子记录笔记"></a>Part 1： 学习别人造好的轮子记录笔记</h2><h3 id="安装"><a href="#安装" class="headerlink" title="安装"></a>安装</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pip3 install -U scidownl</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<a id="more"></a>

<h3 id="使用"><a href="#使用" class="headerlink" title="使用"></a>使用</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">scidownl -h</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="举例子"><a href="#举例子" class="headerlink" title="举例子"></a>举例子</h3><p><strong>Update available links of Scihub</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">scidownl -u</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><strong>Choose scihub url by the index.</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">scidownl -c <span class="number">5</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><strong>List available links of Scihub. You can see the current scihub url is pointing to the 5th scihub url.</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">scidownl -l</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><strong>Download to the current directory</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">scidownl -D <span class="number">10.1021</span>/ol9910114 -o .</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><strong>Download to the specified directory, ie. ‘-o paper’ for downloading to paper directory.</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">scidownl -D <span class="number">10.1021</span>/ol9910114 -o paper</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="批量化"><a href="#批量化" class="headerlink" title="批量化"></a>批量化</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> scidownl.scihub <span class="keyword">import</span> *</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">DOIs = [<span class="string">"10.1038/s41438-020-0303-7"</span>, <span class="string">"10.1038/s41438-020-0298-0"</span>, <span class="string">"10.3389/fgene.2020.00460"</span>]</span><br><span class="line">out = <span class="string">'./paper'</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> doi <span class="keyword">in</span> DOIs:</span><br><span class="line">  SciHub(doi, out).download(choose_scihub_url_index=<span class="number">3</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="Part-2：-通过微信发消息来自动化获取文献"><a href="#Part-2：-通过微信发消息来自动化获取文献" class="headerlink" title="Part 2： 通过微信发消息来自动化获取文献"></a>Part 2： 通过微信发消息来自动化获取文献</h2><p><strong>参考<code>wechat-down-sci.py</code>以下代码：</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> itchat</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> os</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> itchat.content <span class="keyword">import</span> *</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> scidownl.scihub <span class="keyword">import</span> *</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> glob</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> xlwt</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> xlrd</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">path = <span class="string">'./paper'</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">delfile</span><span class="params">(path)</span>:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">#   read all the files under the folder</span></span><br><span class="line">    fileNames = glob.glob(path + <span class="string">r'\*'</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> fileName <span class="keyword">in</span> fileNames:</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">try</span>:</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="comment">#           delete file</span></span><br><span class="line">            os.remove(fileName)</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">except</span>:</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">try</span>:</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="comment"># delete empty folders</span></span><br><span class="line">                os.rmdir(fileName)</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">except</span>:</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="comment"># Not empty, delete files under folders</span></span><br><span class="line">                delfile(fileName)</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="comment"># now, folders are empty, delete it</span></span><br><span class="line">                os.rmdir(fileName)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">delfile(path)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@itchat.msg_register(itchat.content.TEXT)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">text_reply</span><span class="params">(msg)</span>:</span></span><br><span class="line">    message = msg[<span class="string">'Text'</span>]</span><br><span class="line">    mark = <span class="string">'10.'</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> message.startswith(mark) == <span class="literal">True</span>:</span><br><span class="line">        DOI = message</span><br><span class="line">        out = <span class="string">'paper'</span></span><br><span class="line">        sci = SciHub(DOI, out).download(choose_scihub_url_index=<span class="number">3</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        file_dir = <span class="string">'./paper'</span></span><br><span class="line">        os.listdir(file_dir)</span><br><span class="line">        new_workbook = xlwt.Workbook()</span><br><span class="line">        worksheet = new_workbook.add_sheet(<span class="string">'Sheet1'</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        n = <span class="number">0</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> os.listdir(file_dir):</span><br><span class="line">            worksheet.write(n, <span class="number">0</span>, i)</span><br><span class="line">            n += <span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line">        new_workbook.save(<span class="string">'filename.xls'</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        xlsx = xlrd.open_workbook(<span class="string">'filename.xls'</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        table = xlsx.sheet_by_index(<span class="number">0</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        content = str(table.cell_value(<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">0</span>))</span><br><span class="line">        files = os.listdir(file_dir)</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span> f <span class="keyword">in</span> files:</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> content <span class="keyword">in</span> f:</span><br><span class="line">                old_file = os.path.join(file_dir, f)</span><br><span class="line">                new_file = os.path.join(file_dir, <span class="string">'reference.pdf'</span>)</span><br><span class="line">                os.rename(old_file, new_file)</span><br><span class="line">        file_pdf = <span class="string">'./paper/reference.pdf'</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment"># print(file_pdf)</span></span><br><span class="line">        itchat.send_file(file_pdf, msg[<span class="string">'FromUserName'</span>])</span><br><span class="line">        path = <span class="string">'./paper'</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">delfile</span><span class="params">(path)</span>:</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="comment">#   read all the files under the folder</span></span><br><span class="line">            fileNames = glob.glob(path + <span class="string">r'\*'</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">for</span> fileName <span class="keyword">in</span> fileNames:</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">try</span>:</span><br><span class="line">                    <span class="comment">#           delete file</span></span><br><span class="line">                    os.remove(fileName)</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">except</span>:</span><br><span class="line">                    <span class="keyword">try</span>:</span><br><span class="line">                        <span class="comment"># delete empty folders</span></span><br><span class="line">                        os.rmdir(fileName)</span><br><span class="line">                    <span class="keyword">except</span>:</span><br><span class="line">                        <span class="comment"># Not empty, delete files under folders</span></span><br><span class="line">                        delfile(fileName)</span><br><span class="line">                        <span class="comment"># now, folders are empty, delete it</span></span><br><span class="line">                        os.rmdir(fileName)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        delfile(path)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">itchat.auto_login(enableCmdQR=<span class="literal">True</span>, hotReload=<span class="literal">True</span>)</span><br><span class="line">itchat.run()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      <categories>
        <category>Python</category>
        <category>Python自动办公</category>
      </categories>
      <tags>
        <tag>Python</tag>
      </tags>
