  <entry>
    <title>搭建本地blast网页--sequenceserver</title>
    <url>/2020/02/13/%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0blast%E7%BD%91%E9%A1%B5-sequenceserver/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p><strong>目前sequenceserver在搭建本地blast中更受欢迎。使用sequenceserver部署本地化blast网页服务，界面简单易用，还可以同时勾选多个数据库进行比对分析。以下教程使用sequenceserver在ubuntu上搭建。</strong></p>
<a id="more"></a>

<h2 id="step1-1-安装需要Ruby、-RubyGems、-NCBI-BLAST"><a href="#step1-1-安装需要Ruby、-RubyGems、-NCBI-BLAST" class="headerlink" title="step1: 1 安装需要Ruby、 RubyGems、 NCBI BLAST+"></a>step1: 1 安装需要Ruby、 RubyGems、 NCBI BLAST+</h2><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt-get install ruby          </span><br><span class="line">sudo apt-get install gem           </span><br><span class="line">sudo apt-get install ruby-dev      </span><br><span class="line">sudo apt-get install ncbi-blast+</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="step2-安装sequenceserver"><a href="#step2-安装sequenceserver" class="headerlink" title="step2: 安装sequenceserver"></a>step2: 安装sequenceserver</h2><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo gem install sequenceserver</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="step3-sequenceserver建库"><a href="#step3-sequenceserver建库" class="headerlink" title="step3: sequenceserver建库"></a>step3: sequenceserver建库</h2><p>创建一个db(包含nucleotide和protein)数据库，并使用<code>makeblastbd</code>对其建立索引。</p>
<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo makeblastdb -in `nucleotide`.fa -dbtype nucl -out `nucleotide`  ##核酸</span><br><span class="line">sudo makeblastdb -in `protein`.fa -dbtype prot -out `protein`  ##蛋白</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="step4-运行sequenceserver"><a href="#step4-运行sequenceserver" class="headerlink" title="step4: 运行sequenceserver"></a>step4: 运行sequenceserver</h2><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo sequenceserver -d /opt/sequenceserver/db/ -n 16 -p 4567</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>程序运行后，在浏览器中打开 localhost:4567 即可访问本地化blast网页服务。</p>
<p>常用参数：</p>
<blockquote>
<p>-b | –bin<br>    输入ncbi-blast+的bin文件路径<br>-d | –database_dir<br>    输入blast数据库路径<br>-n | –num_threads<br>    设置使用的CPU线程数<br>-p | –port<br>    设置使用的端口号，默认为4567</p>
</blockquote>
]]></content>
      <categories>
        <category>bioinfo</category>
        <category>other</category>
      </categories>
      <tags>
        <tag>bioinfo</tag>
      </tags>
  </entry>
  <entry>
    <title>搭建私有云盘nextcloud</title>
    <url>/2019/12/03/%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E7%A7%81%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%91%E7%9B%98nextcloud/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p><strong><em>安装 NextCloud 18 在 Ubuntu 18 ，另外还需安装 Apache2, MariaDB 和 PHP</em></strong></p>
<a id="more"></a>
<h2 id="Step-1-安装-Apache2"><a href="#Step-1-安装-Apache2" class="headerlink" title="Step 1: 安装 Apache2"></a>Step 1: 安装 Apache2</h2><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt install apache2</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>安装Apache2之后，运行以下命令以禁用目录列表。</p>
<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo sed -i "s/Options Indexes FollowSymLinks/Options FollowSymLinks/" /etc/apache2/apache2.conf</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>接下来，运行以下命令以停止、启动Apache2服务，并启用Apache2服务，使其始终随服务器一起启动。</p>
<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo systemctl stop apache2.service</span><br><span class="line">sudo systemctl start apache2.service</span><br><span class="line">sudo systemctl enable apache2.service</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="Step-2-Install-MariaDB"><a href="#Step-2-Install-MariaDB" class="headerlink" title="Step 2: Install MariaDB"></a>Step 2: Install MariaDB</h2><p>NextCloud还需要一个数据库服务器才能运行。而MariaDB数据库服务器是一个很好的起点。要安装它，请运行以下命令。</p>
<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt-get install mariadb-server mariadb-client</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>安装完成后，可以使用以下命令停止、启动和启用MariaDB服务，使其始终在服务器启动时启动。</p>
<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo systemctl stop mariadb.service</span><br><span class="line">sudo systemctl start mariadb.service</span><br><span class="line">sudo systemctl enable mariadb.service</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>之后，运行以下命令来为MariaDB服务器加密。</p>
<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo mysql_secure_installation</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>出现提示时，请按照以下指南回答问题。</p>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>Enter current password for root (enter for none): Just press the Enter<br>Set root password? [Y/n]; Y<br>New password: ‘password’<br>Re-enter new password: ‘password’<br>Remove anonymous users? [Y/n]; Y<br>Disallow root login remotely? [Y/n]; Y<br>Remove test database and access to it? [Y/n];  Y<br>Reload privilege tables now? [Y/n];  Y</strong></p>
</blockquote>
<p>重启 MariaDB 服务</p>
<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo systemctl restart mariadb.service</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="Step-3-安装-PHP-和相关模块"><a href="#Step-3-安装-PHP-和相关模块" class="headerlink" title="Step 3: 安装 PHP 和相关模块"></a>Step 3: 安装 PHP 和相关模块</h2><p> NextCloud还需要PHP才能运行。</p>
<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt install php -y</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt install libapache2-mod-php -y</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt install php-common -y</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt install libapache2-mod-php -y</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt install php-mbstring -y</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt install php-xmlrpc -y</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt install php-soap -y</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt install php-apcu -y</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt install php-smbclient -y</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt install php-ldap -y</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt install php-redis -y</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt install php-gd -y</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt install php-xml -y</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt install php-intl -y</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt install php-json -y</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt install php-imagick -y</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt install php-mysql -y</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt install php-cli -y</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt install php-mcrypt -y</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt install php-ldap -y</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt install php-zip -y</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt install php-curl -y</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="Step-4-创建-NextCloud-数据库"><a href="#Step-4-创建-NextCloud-数据库" class="headerlink" title="Step 4: 创建 NextCloud 数据库"></a>Step 4: 创建 NextCloud 数据库</h2><p>既然您已经安装了所需的所有软件包，请继续下面的操作，开始配置服务器。首先运行以下命令创建NextCloud数据库。</p>
<p>运行以下命令以登录到数据库服务器。提示输入密码时，键入您在上面创建的MariaDB root密码。</p>
<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo mysql -u root -p</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>然后创建一个数据库叫 nextcloud</p>
<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">CREATE DATABASE nextcloud;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>创建名为nextclouduser的数据库用户并添加密码</p>
<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">CREATE USER 'nextclouduser'@'localhost' IDENTIFIED BY 'new_password_here';</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>然后授予用户对数据库的完全访问权限。</p>
<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">GRANT ALL ON nextcloud.* TO 'nextclouduser'@'localhost' IDENTIFIED BY 'user_password_here' WITH GRANT OPTION;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>最后, 保存并退出</p>
<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">FLUSH PRIVILEGES;</span><br><span class="line">EXIT;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="Step-5-下载-NextCloud-18"><a href="#Step-5-下载-NextCloud-18" class="headerlink" title="Step 5: 下载 NextCloud 18"></a>Step 5: 下载 NextCloud 18</h2><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">unzip nextcloud-18.zip</span><br><span class="line">sudo mv nextcloud /var/www/html/nextcloud/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>然后运行以下命令以设置正确的权限，使NextCloud正常运行。</p>
<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo chown -R www-data:www-data /var/www/html/nextcloud/</span><br><span class="line">sudo chmod -R 755 /var/www/html/nextcloud/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="Step-6-启用NextCloud和重写模块"><a href="#Step-6-启用NextCloud和重写模块" class="headerlink" title="Step 6: 启用NextCloud和重写模块"></a>Step 6: 启用NextCloud和重写模块</h2><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo a2ensite nextcloud.conf</span><br><span class="line">sudo a2enmod rewrite</span><br><span class="line">sudo a2enmod headers</span><br><span class="line">sudo a2enmod env</span><br><span class="line">sudo a2enmod dir</span><br><span class="line">sudo a2enmod mime</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="Step-7-重启-Apache2"><a href="#Step-7-重启-Apache2" class="headerlink" title="Step 7 : 重启 Apache2"></a>Step 7 : 重启 Apache2</h2><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo systemctl restart apache2.service</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
